abstract: Video of Tibetan monk Lobsang Konchok's attempt to kill himself to protest Chinese policies is released; nine Tibetans have set themselves on fire this year, and at least five have died.
snippet: A video of a Tibetan monk’s attempt to kill himself last month by self-immolation to protest Chinese policies has been released.
lead_paragraph: A video of a Tibetan monk’s attempt to kill himself last month by self-immolation to protest Chinese policies has been released.

headline.main: China: Video of Monk’s Protest Released
headline.seo: In China, Video of Tibetan Monk’s Self-Immolation Released
